  "summary": {
    "as": "Reported to House",
    "asOf": "2024-04-26",
    "date": "2024-05-30T18:51:47Z",
    "text": "Plain Language in Contracting Act\n\nThis bill requires that notices of contracting opportunities for small businesses are written in a clear, concise, and accessible manner.\n\nEach notice also must comply with the requirements of the Plain Writing Act of 2010, which are applicable to publications and notices by federal agencies.\n\nThe Small Business Administration must issue rules to implement these requirements."
  },
